{"tid":1516744,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京遊記！Live到上富士山","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T09:35:14.000Z","uid":68777,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"67dd6df638b196f24bf22bb30fe8054422a59d25","tid":1516744,"uid":68777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"大家好，隔左大半年又去東京；照舊窮撚都係搭jetstar凌晨機，今次嘅目標係去富士山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40da30c7e8e24bb694c47357f7f638167a83025d","tid":1516744,"uid":68777,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oR0LqtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR0LqtE.jpg&h=fbe300e7&s={SIZE}\" />上機前指定動作"},{"pid":"4b51c214be18554897d32a70884e462551e52fde","tid":1516744,"uid":58883,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"67dd6df638b196f24bf22bb30fe8054422a59d25","tid":1516744,"uid":68777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"大家好，隔左大半年又去東京；照舊窮撚都係搭jetstar凌晨機，今次嘅目標係去富士山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:17:33.000Z","msg":"我地發起左<span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期日同五罷買</span>！FB已經有２萬人Like左<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">下面有新ＰＯＳＴＥＲ，請廣傳     </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地好需要大家都Like我地FB同簽名去嚮應呀！！</span></span><br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=56957f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\n簽署ＬＩＮＫ 一定要簽 <a href=\"https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbyebuydayhk.github.io%2Fbyebuydayweb%2Fpledge.html&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=2c863bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買可以好有效</span></strong><br />\n如果香港有200萬人=2/7.5人口每星期少2日購物 = 2/7.5*2/7 = 少10%營業額，對鋪租貴既香港地，10%營業額分分鍾就等於商家既50%淨利。另外, 個人消費佔左香港GDP既68%, 如果少10%既消費就等於少左10%既GDP。<br />\n下一季度GPD再負增長,香港將進入Technical Recession。政府冇得唔理。<br />\n<br />\n更加有學者研究指出，罷買只需要全港252,000人集中一日不消費，經濟就會受到好大影響。 (BBC： The '3.5% rule:' How a small minority can change the world.)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買內容（好簡單）</span></strong><br />\n1. 逄星期五、日不花費於日常必須以外的消費<br />\n2. 逄星期五、日不在外食 (上班人士午餐除非可以帶返否則難以避免，但晚餐回家進餐都十分有幫助)<br />\n3. 同時呼籲不光顧抵制清單內的企業，就算買日用品/其他消費都只幫襯良心/本土/外資企業<br />\n4. 呼籲推己及人, 例如絲打比仔仔約逢星期五、日出街食飯，同佢地講逄星期五、日罷買，或只揀良心企業<br />\n由上述基本概念，長遠減低整體消費。<br />\n<br />\n關於我地既報導：<br />\n眾新聞：I Banker（虛構）與網民發起逢周五、日罷買：零成本，希望和理非響應<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zpstHS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zpstHS&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=00fcc29f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zpstHS</a><br />\nＳＣＭＰ既報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U7zPJC&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=9dddb4f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/1ta7DfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ta7DfO.jpg&h=470d5d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/5OkGHHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OkGHHu.jpg&h=ee06cc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9